{"tid":432684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭文字D2 究竟會唔會上映？超過十年了","createTime":"2017-10-11T17:17:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T18:04:57.000Z","uid":137840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3532eb00ae9552b273625d41bba36355694d3cfc","tid":432684,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"本身係頭D 粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為頭D1 電影我先開始追動畫漫畫 到而家Final Stage 同電影Legend 3 都出埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連重野秀一到開始寫第二套跑車作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前14年見寰亞出左條20週年宣傳條片話來年會拍頭D2 果時幾期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/010158_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F010158_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b8b93e46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連周董都話期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/010237_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F010237_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=daec0f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過後尾 劉偉強好似話好多野做 暫時未開拍頭D2 但係就話頭D2 劇本寫好 但係等佢搞埋手頭上其他戲 就會開拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/010642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F010642_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=32379e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連大陸都爆埋演員名單 冇杜汶澤真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/011116_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F011116_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=48e5b3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾仲傳話會用S13 取代AE86 聽到真心屌咗聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家 咩消息都無 最近又話fisherman Lok 同陳冠希又鬧交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/011551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F011551_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=90c0d724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前百度話16年10月上映 最後冇上映到跟住就改左做2017年6月 到而家話未開拍添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n三年啦 真係好期待頭D 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5356b018054b55cc1a498966179655e7bb7d864","tid":432684,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5ae9d34fdee7dd310e1fbae0c82c928c2b93fa","tid":432684,"uid":145019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得任達華做神之手會似d<br />\n佢當年做鄧風比我感覺似係神之手果種冷靜型車手,做神之腳有種格格不入"},{"pid":"08945e69a3873c6eac85b35b5bad18daea73da08","tid":432684,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我覺得任達華做神之手會似d<br />\n佢當年做鄧風比我感覺似係神之手果種冷靜型車手,做神之腳有種格格不入</blockquote><br />\n但係我覺得佢同God Foot 成個餅印咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而我覺得可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb8b8b422a288eea909afb59d93601ea3026f1e","tid":432684,"uid":142725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"成班呀叔呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de440d0f685e1b6a62ac75f5377043a78a99f980","tid":432684,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班呀叔呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff5ade7c7b955bb02d8a18024ac4552e448f1f9","tid":432684,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T18:04:57.000Z","msg":"冇杜文澤 不了"}]}